# Keep the Docker build context small and prevent host artifacts (and secrets)
# from being copied into images. Without this, `COPY backend/ .` pulls the
# host's ~700 MB macOS .venv into the Linux image, and the build context
# includes database backups.
**/.venv
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
frontend/node_modules
frontend/dist
.git
.github
backups
uploads
unknown_faces
logs
database/*.db
docker/models/*.zip
*.log
.env
.DS_Store
scratchpad
